These are Puzzles for 1x4 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-4-1::.
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: june, january, september, november
1. the person who's birthday is in january is in an odd position##4
2. the person who's birthday is in november is between the person who's birthday is in june and the person who's birthday is in january##2
3. the person who's birthday is in november is on the right of the person who's birthday is in june##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2    |    3    |  4   |
| Birthday   | june | november | january | september |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-4-2::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: scientific, zombie, crime, spy
1. the person watching scientific movies is on the left of the person watching spy movies##1
2. the person watching zombie movies is in an odd position##4
3. the person watching zombie movies is on the left or right of the person watching scientific movies##3

.:: Answer ::.
|        |   1    |    2    |   3    |   4   |
| Movie-Genre   | zombie | scientific | spy | crime |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-4-3::.
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: surfing, lacrosse, tennis, cycling
1. the person who's sport is cycling is on the left or right of the person who's sport is surfing##3
2. the person who's sport is surfing is in an odd position##4
3. the person who's sport is tennis is between the person who's sport is cycling and the person who's sport is lacrosse##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |   2    |    3    |      4       |
| Sport   | surfing | cycling | tennis | lacrosse |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-4-4::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: fishing, card-games, camping, chess
