2. the person who's hobby is camping is in an even position##4
3. the person who's hobby is chess is between the person who's hobby is fishing and the person who's hobby is camping##2

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1       |    2     |       3       |   4    |
| Hobby   | card-games | fishing | chess | camping |

