.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-4-12::.
4 different pets are kept: hedgehog, turtle, guinea-pig, bird
1. the owner of the hedgehog is on the right of the owner of the bird##1
2. the owner of the bird is on the right of the owner of the turtle##1
3. the owner of the turtle is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|             |    1    |   2    |  3  |    4    |
| Pet   | guinea-pig | turtle | bird | hedgehog |

