.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-4-19::.
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: havana, siglo, fonseca, bluemaster
1. the siglo-smoker is the siglo-smoker##1
2. the bluemaster-smoker is on the left or right of the fonseca-smoker##3
3. the fonseca-smoker is on the far left or far right##3
4. the havana-smoker is in an even position##4
5. the bluemaster-smoker is on the left of the siglo-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|        |     1     |     2      |   3   |    4    |
| Cigar   | fonseca | bluemaster | siglo | havana |

