.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-4-20::.
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: august, october, september, march
1. the person who's birthday is in september is in an odd position##4
2. the person who's birthday is in march is on the left of the person who's birthday is in september##1
3. the person who's birthday is in september is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in october##3

.:: Answer ::.
|       |    1    |         2          |    3    |    4     |
| Birthday   | august | march | september | october |

 